http://www.international-auto.com/fuel-and-emissions-systems/bosch-fuel-injection-air-hoses.cfm

Enter "1986 AlfaRomeo GTV-6" to see the pricing on this kit.
$16 buys you two each of
a short fuel line, a screw hose clamp and a press-on hose clamp
for the injector end of the hose.  You'll need two kit$ which may
blow your tight budget.  However, I could not find the clamps
elsewhere.  YMMV

